You are clearly

39:44.275 --> 39:46.008
a danger to society.

39:47.945 --> 39:50.012
Oh, my God. Somebody help!

39:50.014 --> 39:52.114
Oh, my God. Help!

39:52.116 --> 39:54.883
You think the world didn't exist

39:54.885 --> 39:57.519
before you were born?!

39:57.521 --> 40:00.522
You've suffered nothing!

40:00.524 --> 40:02.458
You have no idea

40:02.460 --> 40:06.328
what it's like to be gutted!

40:06.330 --> 40:10.232
To scrape yourself
up off the floor!

40:10.234 --> 40:12.868
I matter!

40:24.048 --> 40:26.482
(panting)

40:44.168 --> 40:45.768
(sighs softly)

40:48.339 --> 40:49.738
Oh.

40:53.911 --> 40:55.744
Shit!

40:55.746 --> 40:57.813
(laughs)

40:59.850 --> 41:00.949
Well, hello.

41:00.951 --> 41:03.085
What are you
doing here?

41:03.087 --> 41:05.954
How'd you get in?

41:05.956 --> 41:08.023
How'd I get in?

41:10.928 --> 41:13.429
You practically
dragged me up here.

41:15.399 --> 41:17.433
Or don't you remember it
that way?

41:20.771 --> 41:22.438
(Sally laughing)

41:39.723 --> 41:41.390
(panting)

41:41.392 --> 41:43.959
(lighter clicks)

41:49.633 --> 41:51.233
You need to go.

41:54.104 --> 41:55.437
What?

41:55.439 --> 41:57.806
You need to go.

41:57.808 --> 42:00.943
Oh, you prick.

42:00.945 --> 42:04.513
You're gonna pull that shit
after the things we did?

42:09.286 --> 42:11.820
Something real happened here.

42:11.822 --> 42:14.756
And it wasn't a dream.

42:14.758 --> 42:17.159
I don't remember anything.

42:19.096 --> 42:21.930
Anything at all.

42:23.934 --> 42:27.035
You're a goddamn liar.

42:27.037 --> 42:29.838
Oh, yes, you are.
You remember everything.

42:29.840 --> 42:32.941
Everything you did.

42:36.180 --> 42:38.714
And it's gonna happen again.

42:38.716 --> 42:41.617
And again and again.

42:41.619 --> 42:43.852
And you can't stop it.

42:43.854 --> 42:46.755
'Cause it's our destiny.

42:49.693 --> 42:52.060
And you can't fight destiny.

43:02.039 --> 43:04.106
(door closes)

43:06.076 --> 43:08.143
(elevator bell dings)

43:09.079 --> 43:10.579
I want to thank you, Liz.

43:10.581 --> 43:12.381
Sincerely.

43:12.383 --> 43:14.883
Your words truly
resonated with me.

43:14.885 --> 43:15.884
Aw.

43:15.886 --> 43:18.086
That's sweet
of you, doll.

43:18.088 --> 43:20.856
No, really.

43:20.858 --> 43:23.091
I feel changed.

43:23.093 --> 43:25.160
Deeply.

43:25.162 --> 43:26.862
(chuckles)

43:26.864 --> 43:28.163
Finally.

43:28.165 --> 43:29.898
(both laugh)

43:29.900 --> 43:31.900
Well, I did think
you might let the girl

43:31.902 --> 43:34.169
at the Lancôme counter
give you a makeover.

43:34.171 --> 43:36.905
But... sure,
this is good, too.

43:36.907 --> 43:39.274
You think I went too far.

43:39.276 --> 43:41.009
Not at all.

43:42.746 --> 43:46.415
Not... at... all.

43:58.529 --> 44:00.462
Oh.

44:00.464 --> 44:02.364
I hope this isn't plasma.

44:02.366 --> 44:05.233
This red is the Grenache blend

44:05.235 --> 44:07.469
(laughs): they never had
a chance to finish.

44:07.471 --> 44:09.104
Ooh.

44:12.643 --> 44:15.577
Well, I guess
I've come through it.

44:15.579 --> 44:17.779
(sighs)

44:17.781 --> 44:18.947
In fact,
I'm sure of it.

44:18.949 --> 44:20.315
Sure of what, honey?

44:20.317 --> 44:22.784
It's ironic.
Hmm?

44:22.786 --> 44:25.854
But I never knew how
to live until I died.

44:31.328 --> 44:34.229
That dress
fits you so well.

44:34.231 --> 44:36.832
Always been one of
my favorites.

44:37.768 --> 44:39.267
Holden,

44:39.269 --> 44:42.838
doesn't your mother
look pretty?

44:42.840 --> 44:44.906
Give her a little kiss.

44:59.757 --> 45:02.257
Mommy...

45:02.259 --> 45:04.493
you're just like me now.

45:06.463 --> 45:09.464
Yes, baby.

45:09.466 --> 45:11.833
I'm just like you.

45:11.835 --> 45:13.869
Does that mean
you'll stay with me forever?

45:13.871 --> 45:15.871
As long as your mommy
obeys the rules,

45:15.873 --> 45:19.474
she can stay as
long as she likes.

45:19.476 --> 45:21.977
It's very simple.

45:21.979 --> 45:25.147
You'll care for the children,
bathe them,

45:25.149 --> 45:28.316
keep them out of harm's way
as their new governess.

45:28.318 --> 45:30.986
The old one was
terrible for years.

45:30.988 --> 45:34.356
I should've removed
her long ago.

45:34.358 --> 45:37.025
Of course,
if you feel

45:37.027 --> 45:39.561
this burden's
too much to bear...

45:40.397 --> 45:41.897
No.

45:41.899 --> 45:44.332
No, it's no burden.

45:44.334 --> 45:45.500
Marvelous.

45:45.502 --> 45:46.902
Then it's settled.

45:46.904 --> 45:49.538
John lives in the hotel.

45:52.209 --> 45:54.476
I haven't told him anything.

45:54.478 --> 45:56.511
What if he sees me?

45:56.513 --> 45:59.414
You'd be amazed,
the wondrous possibilities

45:59.416 --> 46:03.752
that can begin
with a simple hello.

46:03.754 --> 46:05.721
(chuckles softly)

46:05.723 --> 46:07.923
Now, Holden,

46:07.925 --> 46:10.926
I believe it's past
your bedtime, darling.

46:10.928 --> 46:13.161
But we've only had
a minute together.

46:13.163 --> 46:16.098
You misunderstand, Alex.

46:17.935 --> 46:21.570
You and Holden
will have...

46:21.572 --> 46:23.505
<i> forever.</i>

46:23.507 --> 46:25.574
¶ ¶

46:49.967 --> 46:52.033
¶ ¶

47:11.622 --> 47:13.688
(coffin closes)
